{"tid":113082,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[厭世JJ]有無人成日抱住一種兩老離開就跟住走既念頭","createTime":"2017-02-08T15:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T14:58:41.000Z","uid":34356,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84458e675c8e583591aeaaceb94423ab7423bf50","tid":113082,"uid":34356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"對生活好厭倦無熱情<br />\n返工放工然後對住四幅牆<br />\n交流得最多既係同事或客人<br />\n<br />\n而家連打機都變得無興趣,望住個mom發牛豆<br />\n一諗到未來身邊個個朋友都結哂婚,自己放工 節目 放大假都係孤零零<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我真係唔想黎到呢個世界,好挫好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係抱住唔想白頭人送黑頭人既念頭生存<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家睇完呢篇廢嗡, 過多排可能會睇下精神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7158a3ecc4bcc9b12099cefbc7ee669ae632c0c5","tid":113082,"uid":14083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:14:16.000Z","msg":"同我一樣"},{"pid":"c64fc1aab381428fac61f39baa5b14aed86472bd","tid":113082,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"暫時係"},{"pid":"ca479ef7c8f41e13829c51915d5d4f49b74656d1","tid":113082,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:28:48.000Z","msg":"心想事成 萬事如意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7bbfbe1eb7b1019325c45e14c0e1546ce7c63c","tid":113082,"uid":16005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T18:35:19.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf2557e260d0c2e901b246602b99878893725a4","tid":113082,"uid":71893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:01:02.000Z","msg":"我一直都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488f05a65ed14bc20131a1709e82ad9410e6b1f5","tid":113082,"uid":31651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:04:27.000Z","ms