0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇乜好熟既朋友<br />\n冇拖拍<br />\n冇錢冇資產<br />\n<br />\n屋企人唔係度之後我對呢個世界都唔會再有任何眷戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3424eec380464d0a8205c3ce01d3ddf63cdb0b3","tid":113082,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90eeff7ee458d4931251c8af68ccbb0bb3774f7e","tid":113082,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0654fdf1b739d74d8e517e7dcf9a7423c30c714c","tid":113082,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:55:15.000Z","msg":"我同樓主一樣諗法<br />\n等屋企人自自然然過世<br />\n<br />\n我應該會燒炭死<br />\n做人真係好攰<br />\n但我冇權去揀自己出唔出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15519d5f164bd184bc5c77f34f94a95afe54d1c0","tid":113082,"uid":34356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同樓主一樣諗法<br />\n等屋企人自自然然過世<br />\n<br />\n我應該會燒炭死<br />\n做人真係好攰<br />\n但我冇權去揀自己出唔出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果自己組織左個家庭<br />\n我會好想睇到個仔仔女女長大,成家立室,俾到父幹佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等佢行少d彎路<br />\n當正公主大少咁養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可惜連另一半都無<br />\n<br />\n自己又無錢無外表無父幹,憑咩